data.description: You will fall in love with this peaceful setting located on a corner lot near Keystone Lake. Home offers a Huge country kitchen, 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths and a large primary bedroom. Relax on the front deck and listen to nature. Bring your toys home. Has a 2 car carport plus storage buildings and additional RV or boat parking. And a Storm Cellar!
